V---***-TABLE DOSSIER PRINCIPALE TBDOPRN-***

V DELETE FROM RDEU.TBDOPRN                                                      
V WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM RDEU.TBEXDOS                                      
V                 WHERE TEXDNFOY    = TDPRNFOY                                  
V                 AND   TEXDNCONT   = TDPRNCONT                                 
V                 AND   TEXDNCARTE  = TDPRNCARTE

V AND   TEXDCTRAIT  = 'D');                                                     
V COMMIT;

V   A.TVDNOMSOC,                                                                
V   A.TVDAGR,                                                                   
V   A.TVDADRSOC,                                                                
V   A.TVDVILSOC,                                                                
V   A.TVDCPTTSOC,                                                               
V   A.TVDTELSOC,                                                                
V   ( SELECT B.TBVCIBAN                                                         
V     FROM RDEU.TBVDBQE B                                                       
V     WHERE A.TVDSOC = B.TBVSOC                                                 
V     AND A.TVDAGR = B.TBVAGR                                                   
V     AND B.TBVRANG = 1),                                                       
V   ( SELECT C.TBVCIBAN                                                         
V     FROM RDEU.TBVDBQE C                                                       
V     WHERE A.TVDSOC = C.TBVSOC                                                 
V     AND A.TVDAGR = C.TBVAGR                                                   
V     AND C.TBVRANG = 2),                                                       
V   ( SELECT D.TBVCIBAN                                                         
V     FROM RDEU.TBVDBQE D                                                       
V     WHERE A.TVDSOC = D.TBVSOC                                                 
V     AND A.TVDAGR = D.TBVAGR                                                   
V     AND D.TBVRANG = 3),                                                       
V   A.TVDCPOSA,                                                                 
V   A.TVDSOC                                                                    
V  FROM RDEU.TBVDVDR A                                                          
V  ;

V//SYSIN    DD  DATA,DLM=#$                                                     
V   SELECT   TDPRNFOY,                                                          
V            TDPRNCONT,                                                         
V            TDPRNCARTE,                                                        
V            TDPRNDT,                                                           
V            TDPRDPOSA,                                                         
V            (TDPRMCRD - TDPRMSREC),                                            
V            TDOCCCONTVERF,

V       AND  TDPRNDT     = TDOCNDT                                              
V       AND  TDOCNRANG   = 1                                                    
V                                                                               
V       AND  TDPRCPOSA = 'FI2'                                                  
V       AND  TDPRMCRD > 0                                                       
V       AND  TDPRMSREC >= 0                                                     
V       AND  TDPRMCRD > TDPRMSREC                                               
V       ;                                                                       
V#$

V  SORT FROM(TEMP2) TO(OUTDD4) USING(FLT3)
